lead_paragraph: After a fourth successive 1-0 victory sent Leicester into a seven-point lead, some giddy fans started to unfurl Premier League "champions" scarves in the King Power Stadium.

headline.print_headline: Leicester 7 Points in Front a Year After Being 7 From Safety
